== Related fields ==
Biostatistics shares several methods with quantitative fields such as:
* [[computational biology]]
*[[computer science]],
*[[operations research]],
*[[psychometrics]],
*[[statistics]],
*[[econometrics]], and
*mathematical [[demography]]

