The [[Hebrew Bible]] is the [[Tanakh]] of [[Judaism]]. Judaism does not accept or use the term &quot;[[Old Testament]]&quot;, nor does it recognize the [[deuterocanonical books]] or the [[New Testament]] of [[Christianity]] as [[Biblical canon|canonical]].

