* [[The Blowfish]], a satirical newspaper at Brandeis University
* [[Blowfish (cipher)]], encryption algorithm
* [[Blowfish (company)]], American erotic goods supplier
* [[Columbia Blowfish]], baseball team
* [[Hootie &amp; the Blowfish]]
