&lt;gallery&gt;
Image:Standing_Bodhisattva_Gandhara_Musee_Guimet.jpg|Standing bodhisattva. [[Gandhara|Gandhāra]], 2nd-3rd century.
Image:Museum für Indische Kunst Dahlem Berlin Mai 2006 006.jpg|Standing bodhisattva. Gandhāra, 2nd-3rd century.
Image:Mural Worshipping Bodhisattva.jpg|Gathering of bodhisattvas. China, 6th century.
Image:Mural Avolokitesvara.jpg|Mural of bodhisattvas. China, [[Tang Dynasty]].
Image:Kokūzō Bosatsu.jpg|[[Akasagarbha|Ākāśagarbha]] Bodhisattva. Japan, 9th century.
Image:Chinese mural of a bodhisattva, ink and color on plaster, c. 952, Honolulu Academy of Arts.jpg|Mural of a bodhisattva. China, 10th century.
Image:WLA brooklynmuseum Seated Avalokitesvara black chlorite.jpg|[[Avalokitesvara|Avalokiteśvara]] Bodhisattva. India, 11th-12th century.
Image:Mahasthamaprapta.jpg|[[Mahasthamaprapta|Mahāsthāmaprāpta]] Bodhisattva. China, 13th century.
Image:Monju crossing the sea.jpg|[[Manjusri|Mañjuśrī]] Bodhisattva crossing the sea. Japan, 14th century.
Image:Jizo, the Bodhisattva of the Earth Matrix.jpg|[[Ksitigarbha|Kṣitigarbha]] Bodhisattva. Japan, 15th century.
